{"tid":2063280,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"有冇人好中意聽唱見既歌？","createTime":"2020-06-13T20:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T12:09:20.000Z","uid":76225,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac3e9eacf362dada56896ad675515a4eef3f931d","tid":2063280,"uid":76225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20:04:28.000Z","msg":"一直都好中意聽唔同唱見既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但好似冇咩人討論咁<br />\n平時會同一首歌聽唔同人演繹同埋睇歌詞講咩<br />\n好中意日本果種作詞風格 好似睇緊說明文咁樣<br />\n最近不停loop緊下面果兩首<br />\n本身聽唔慣mafumafu既高音 後來聽佢原創歌之後發覺佢係唱作全能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人覺得佢唱得最好聽既係佢自己作既歌 佢既翻唱唔知點解聽落都好似怪怪地咁<br />\n或者有其他好聽既歌都可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qekw-BDMazM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQekw-BDMazM&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=07ca045e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qekw-BDMazM</a><br />\nしゅーず把聲帶有磁性 勁好J 本人都好靚仔(highway lover有顏出)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a4nyTLlbEYY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Da4nyTLlbEYY&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJjsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=dce63e1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a4nyTLlbEYY</a><br />\n可惜身邊冇咩人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2e5277085c46327c28e530a70327fb20b7ca85","tid":2063280,"uid":180181,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T20:21:58.000Z","msg":"聽香港嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JZmo2jx_Q4U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F